    'body' => 'On 01/08/99 at 09:19 AM,  Rob_Prior@nynet.nybe.on.ca (Rob Prior) said:

>"MJ Dougherty" <martinjd@globalnet.co.uk> writes:
>>There\'s a tendency (especially, I seem to recall among teenage gamers) to
