Nope. That\'s 
1 million phones = 1 megaphone
1 millionth phone = 1 microphone

>2000 mockingbirds = two kilomockingbirds
>10 cards = 1 decacards
>10 millipedes = 1 centipede
Yep. Checks with my source.

