Base Temp 86 + Lat Mod -12 = 74
Summer Plus +23.4 x Axial Tilt mod 1 = +23.4
Daytime Plus +5.4
Orbit Ecc Plus 0
Highest Possible Temp = 74+23.4+5.4+0 = 102.8 degrees C

