6 - Population rating
7 - Population value (population = value * 10^rating)
8 - Starport
9 - Political type
A - Control Rating (public safety)
B - Tech level
C - Allegiance
D - Bases
E - World Trade Number
F - Trade Codes
G - Number of gas giants present (+ if greater than 9)
H - Number of planetoid belts present (+ if greater than 9)

